  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by a square jaw and a broken line of cartilage across the nose. Brown eyes sit deep under heavy brows, set in a face creased by habitual squinting and long hours under harsh light. Black hair is kept in a close, practical pixie cut that exposes the ears and accentuates a high, slightly ridged hairline. Bronze skin shows ingrained calluses at the knuckles and faint old burn-freckling along the forearms consistent with years working near open heat.",
